================================================================================
RECOMMENDATIONS:
================================================================================

1. Add <script src='theory-constants.js'></script> to each HTML file header
2. Replace magic numbers with PM.category.constant references
3. For formulas, use PM.format.scientific() for display formatting
4. Prioritize fixing OUTDATED values first
5. Use agents/AI to automate the replacement process

Example replacements:
  - '2.118e16' → PM.proton_decay.M_GUT
  - '47.2' → PM.pmns_matrix.theta_23
  - '-0.853' → PM.dark_energy.w0_PM
  - '144' → PM.topology.chi_eff
